"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:12:36.000Z","msg":"大馬新聞真係冠絕港台中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd5f4e87b4cc87537f6ba5a5fb9741ffa9d6754","tid":928864,"uid":143556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:15:41.000Z","msg":"甜故嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94cba8480d92a0467639c3efec0ee9c65c19cea","tid":928864,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d807cde5e72b958fbcf91579daeacc43ca2ca2f","tid":928864,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:49:38.000Z","msg":"都話工程俾狗做<br />\n辛苦完仲要被人屌"},{"pid":"f93d76677c631d13ccd5fb5f67979b018160b0f1","tid":928864,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e93fd0fdc8dc3734e821affe7e2a3d618ce86b5e","tid":928864,"uid":161207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T07:14:28.000Z","msg":"2018年11月30日<br />\n<br />\n（哈拉雷30日綜合電）津巴布韋一名29歲女子，2年前和37歲黑哥交往，當然不時在夜間進行深入淺出的高強度隧道工程。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但女子今年5月單方面分手後，還控告前男友，因為他的隧道挖掘機過於巨大，導致她本來小橋流水的通幽曲徑，被擴展成6車道的海底隧道。 &ldquo;彈性疲乏&rdquo;的她現在希望男方負擔醫療費用，讓她進行戰後重建。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《都市報》報導，兩人交往當時，黑哥克里馬已經有家室，但曼捷娜仍願意當他的小三，兩人也展開一段熱火激情，隧道工程如火如荼進行。<br />\n<br />\n但曼捷娜說，原本人跡罕至的她&ldquo;非常緊緻&rdquo;，克里馬卻異於常人，他那密度式隧道挖掘機，是一款能有效在高密度地質實施挖掘的高科技設備，就算你是硬度7級的花崗岩，也會在連震帶鑽下土崩瓦解，地下水湧泉而出。<br />\n<br />\n曼捷娜就抱怨，多次隧道工程之後，她的隧道被過度開發，這也是兩人在今年5月分手的主因。<br />\n<br />\n曼捷娜也說，自從她被克里馬挖掘後，再也有沒有其他男性工程師，能填補她那在山風中嗚嗚作響的隧道。<br />\n<br />\n現在曼捷娜決定檢討工程，找工程師將隧道級別縮小。她希望克里馬負擔醫療費用，曼捷娜估計手術費用需約15萬蘭特幣(約4.6萬令吉)，目前克里馬尚未回應。<br />\n<br />\n文：非洲部<br />\n<br />\n寫新聞條友係咪癡q咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:52:54.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"27395c0cef2483b6d88e5f38704e4db3918d371f","tid":928864,"uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"Once you go black, you never go back."},{"pid":"ebae314938c8fe2d9fa9d41da077ec540af6b6e4","tid":928864,"uid":167118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T08:00:39.000Z","msg":"high咗嘢"},{"pid":"0c336d82ababb7c48d5553141b878a0eef41f68a","tid":928864,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T08:44:10.000Z","msg":"戰後重建<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}